data.text: @ScottGideon3 Exactly! It's just so dumb and wrong

@ScottGideon3 I am completely astounded that the 1993 accusation is accepted as fact. The only difference between now and the renewed accusation in 2014 is that she went on television and turned on the crocodile tears. Because nobody reads anymore, voila. It’s a “fact.” “I saw it on tv.”

@ScottGideon3 I wish he would hold a press conference or have his lawyer hold one. Or that he would have one together with Moses and even take questions. In this day and age, you cannot leave these accusations unanswered. Whether it’s trial by media or not.
@ScottGideon3 Although I get that they would have trouble selling tickets because of Rosemary’s baby’s army.
@ScottGideon3 Check this spineless theatre’s news: https://t.co/P4UKyRpGmI
